						               													<description>Le quiz de comment (The How? quiz) is an educational trivia game aimed for kids.&amp;#10;Each player starts with 7 cards in 7 different categories. The goal of the game is to get rid of the cards a quickly as possible and score most points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One by one the players play out a card with either a solo or group question. The solo question has to be answered by the player. If right he scores a point, otherwise he draws a new card of the same category. &amp;#10;All players can try to answer the group question simultaneously. The quickest scores two points. If a person gives a wrong answer he draws a new card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when a player has no cards left. The one with most points wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
